M|Red |it|cr worktree w/o verifying it's ignored (project-local)
M|Red |it|Skip baseline tst verification
M|Red |it|Proceed w/ failing tests w/o asking
M|Red |it|Assume directory location when ambiguous
M|Red |it|Skip CLAUDE.md check
